      <h2 class="text-sm text-primary tracking-widest font-bold title-font uppercase mb-1">
        My Skills
      </h2>
      <h3 class="max-w-prose mx-auto leading-relaxed text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-200">
        What I've learned throughout my journey so far
